Edit 'MAGJACK-POE.pac';
Description '\
<h3>PoE Compatible MagJack</h3>\n\
This RJ-45 jack with magnetics has 10 pins, gives you access to the unused twisted pair (10BASE-T, and 100BASE-T) which usually carries power in a power-over-ethernet system.\n\
<br>\n\
<br>\n\
<b>Footprint is Proven</b>';
